{
  "texts": [
    "In the second pass, 34 more sentences were translated and we ended up with a total of 174 untranslated sentences, which represents about 23% of the entire dataset.",
    "Our quantitative analysis focused on these 174 untranslated sentences.",
    "We extracted the safety rating information for each sentence and plotted the severity and probability scores.",
    "We studied the relationship between how severe the predicted harm in a given sentence is with how confident the model is with its assessment.",
    "Additionally, we realized that each sentence can be blocked for one, two, three, or all four categories."
  ]
}